channel.title: How to: Fix unpacking error 86 with SWAT's new emote system
channel.description:
Getting the unpacking error 86? Don't be discouraged!
[b]Difficulty: 2/10 if you're new, 1/10 if you aren't[/b] [b]Boredom Level: Extremely High[/b] [b]Classes Edited: 20, 23, 35, and 36[/b]
[color=red][center]Step 1:[/center] [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?g3nmgm5wxzw]Download Pack 86 [/url]
Open the file. You may want to extract it so that it's easier to navigate. [color=red][center]Step 2:[/center] Now, replace your class 20, 23, 35, and 36 with the ones provided. Don't worry, they shouldn't down your client. Note; Always make backups of your client(s) before adding something big or new.
Now, incase you're wondering, the bandos gfx in class 20 has nothing to do with this tutorial. (At least not much :P)
Just run you're client and it should be up and working :) It's a pretty simple fix.
Credits: Pb600 Me
Post your errors if u do get any (you shouldn't but whatever)
